  "texts": [
    "Other enhancement mechanisms such as random walk based on Levy flights and chaotic map-based swarm initialization are also exploited to increase search robustness.",
    "Related studies of neural architecture and hyperparameter search using the Sparrow Search Algorithm were also investigated in [31].",
    "A Tree Seed Algorithm was exploited by Kiran [34].",
    "A swarm of tree solutions is randomly initialized.",
    "For each tree, a number of seed solutions are generated."
